<section class="hero-ent">
  <div class="container hero-ent-inner">
    <div class="hero-ent-content">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Enterprise</span>

      <h1 class="hero-ent-headline">
        Para empresas que<br />exigem senioridade
      </h1>

      <p class="hero-ent-sub">
        Empresas com estrutura consolidada precisam de um parceiro técnico à
        altura da operação. Não de um fornecedor que executa escopo e some.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-ent-ctas">
        <a href="/contato" class="btn-hero-primary">Falar com a gente →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-ent {
    background-color: var(--bg-hero);
    background-image: url('/BG-SITE.png');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    height: 710px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-ent-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .hero-ent-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .hero-ent-headline {
    font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 80px);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 0.97;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: #fff;
    text-wrap: unset;
  }

  .hero-ent-sub {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    margin-top: var(--space-5);
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 750px;
  }

  .hero-ent-ctas {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: var(--space-5);
  }

  .btn-hero-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 13px 28px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    white-space: nowrap;
    background: #0A0A0A;
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    border-bottom: none;
    transition: background var(--dur-fast) var(--ease);
  }
  .btn-hero-primary:hover {
    background: #212121;
    color: #fff;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-ent {
      height: auto;
      min-height: 600px;
      padding: var(--space-8) 0;
    }
  }
</style>
